name: Joytale Personalized Dog Collars with Engraved Name Plate, Silent No Jingle Custom Nylon Collar with Fixed ID Tag, Reflective Soft Neoprene Padded Breathable for Medium Dogs, Purple
short_description: Silent & Secure Identification - No More Jingling Noise: Say goodbye to noisy, jingling tags that wake you up at night. Unlike traditional hanging tags that can get caught or fall off, our laser-etched stainless steel nameplate is fixed securely flat on the collar. This silent design provides peace of mind, ensuring your dog's ID stays permanently attached while keeping your home quiet and your pet distraction-free

Maximum Visibility for Night Safety - Premium Reflective Nylon: Keep your furry friend visible and safe during late-night or early-morning walks. Constructed with high durability nylon and highly reflective stitching, this collar reflects ambient light to alert passing vehicles and pedestrians. It offers the perfect balance of heavy duty strength for pullers and essential safety visibility for outdoor adventures

Anti Chafe Comfort - Soft Neoprene Padded Lining: Designed for all-day wear without irritation. The collar features a luxurious, breathable Neoprene padding that creates a soft cushion between the rugged nylon and your dog's neck. This design protects sensitive skin and prevents fur damage, allowing your pet to run, play, and sleep in absolute comfort

Clear & Fade-Resistant Customization - Identifying Your Lost Pet: Ensure your lost dog can always find their way home. We use advanced laser engraving technology to etch your customized text deep into the stainless steel plate, making it clear, readable, and fade-resistant over years of use. With space for up to 4 lines of text, you can include your dog’s name, phone number, and address—crucial info that speaks for them when they can't

Perfect Fit for Every Breed - Adjustable & Measured Sizing: A tailored fit for every stage, from growing puppies to large breeds. Available in 5 adjustable sizes (XS to XL), suitable for boys and girls of all breeds. Please measure your dog's neck circumference before ordering to ensure the most comfortable fit. The high-quality buckle ensures the collar stays on securely, whether playing in the park or resting at home
